Mafina BV of Voorburg, a subsidiary ofPetrofina SA &lt;PETB.BR>, is issuing a minimum 200 mln francseven year bond with warrants, paying two pct, lead managerCredit Suisse said.    The issue is guaranteed by the Belgian parent.    The warrant exercise period is from May 1, 1987 until May20, 1991. Each 5,000 franc note carries nine warrannts, each ofwhich entitles the holder to buy one share in the company at10,800 Belgian francs each.    Payment is due April 30. REUTER&#3;